snippet.textDisplay:
@Hisotrygeek94 I agree with both of you. What really pisses me off is that ScrewAttack love taking great pleasure in beating up poor Ecco.
After several criticisms for his thoughts on the first Ecco game, Craig's response was a highly sarcastic view on the sequel, Tides of Time.
To summarise it: "Oh man, I'm so sorry for bashing Ecco. This game is actually good for all of this awesome stuff. No, Ecco sucks."

